Screaming Vlog 37 starts off in Sunny San Diego where we link with @jeremeknibbs, @8ballr and @k3vinbraun at a gnarly street gap. After making some friends, we keep the session rolling to City Heights Skatepark to meet up with the rest of the squad! We’ve got @jake_wooten, @ericdressen, @emangrizzle1, SC Team Manager @instapizzle & Master Lensmen @_nickhanson and @thekillatapes in the mix for some good old fashioned fun in the sun. As the session fires up, Jake unleashes the Switch Hurricane as seen in his Thrasher part. You definitely won't want to miss this one! Hit our @youtube channel to watch now! Where should we go in the next Screaming Vlog? Let us know in the comments!

Today we are stoked to be joined by SC Pros @maurcoy and @blakeular to talk about and put to the test the 7.8 x 31.5 Screaming Hand Deck! This board features smaller measurements, so if you have a smaller frame, this board will feel great! This one also has a 13.5in wheelbase for getting those spins and flips whipped around with consistency. Be sure to stop by your local shop and see if they have this one available. We put Santa Cruz Skateboards Brand Manager @andrewcannon to the test with three ALL NEW challenges to find out how this setup skates! Hit up our @youtube channel to watch now, then let us know in the comments below what challenges we should throw in the bins next!
👉 Andrew's product setup:
7.8 x 31 'Screaming Hand’ Deck
129 Standard Stage 11 @independenttrucks 
53mm 99A @rictawheels Speed Rings
@bronsonspeedco G3s 🏁💨
7/8ths Indy Allen Bolts
Black Mob Grip

For our latest installment of '30 Minutes With', we link up with @tomasta at Middletown Skatepark! Watching Tom's footage is always a treat, but in this '30 Minutes With' we get to see just how dialed and consistent Tom is on any given day. We are joined by Santa Cruz Brand Manager @andrewcannon & Tom's good friend @bigneck who does an amazing job handling hosting duties while all the ripping is captured by Master Lensmen @thekillatapes and @trevarcushing! Hit our @youtube channel to watch now. Where should we pull up for our next ’30 Minutes With’? Let us know in the comments!
🎬: @ericdanescu
#SantaCruzSkateboards
